class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"></span> </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-4 mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<div class=\"block pink position-relative\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\"><a class=\"stretched-link full-width\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/settle-canada/language-skills.html\">Learn English or French</a></h3>\n<p class=\"mrgn-bttm-lg\">Get resources to help you improve your English or French. <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-comments fa-3x pstn-bttm-xs pstn-rght-xs mrgn-rght-lg mrgn-bttm-md icon-pink\"></span></p>\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"></span> </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-4 mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<div class=\"block pink position-relative\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\"><a class=\"stretched-link full-width\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/settle-canada/driving.html\">Driving in Canada</a></h3>\n<p class=\"mrgn-bttm-lg\">Learn about driver’s licenses, road rules and car insurance. <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-car fa-3x pstn-bttm-xs pstn-rght-xs mrgn-rght-lg mrgn-bttm-md icon-pink\"></span></p>\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"></span> </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-4 mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<div class=\"block pink position-relative\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\"><a class=\"stretched-link full-width\" href=\"/en/revenue-agency/services/tax/international-non-residents/individuals-leaving-entering-canada-non-residents/newcomers-canada-immigrants.html\">Your first tax year</a></h3>\n<p class=\"mrgn-bttm-lg\">Learn about your first tax year, benefits and credits. <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-money-bill fa-3x pstn-bttm-xs pstn-rght-xs mrgn-rght-lg mrgn-bttm-md icon-pink\"></span></p>\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"></span> </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6 mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<div class=\"block gray padding-10\">\n<div class=\"row d-flex\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-11 col-sm-11